{"title":"vps+telegram搭建rss订阅机器人","date":"2019-08-10T12:17:51.000Z","link":"post/my-sixth-blog","updated":"2019-08-10T12:31:18.179Z","content":"<p>因为自己有vps，总想忙活一些稀奇玩意<del>（不然更新什么呢）</del>，但是我最近比较忙，目前只看到这个，就尝试一下，加上总是忘了番剧看到那，rsshub又可以订阅某个人关注的番剧了所以，开始吧</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>用的是<a href=\"https://www.vpsgo.com/telegram-rssbot.html\" title=\"这位\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">这位</a>的教程</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h4 id=\"申请电报机器人啦-发送\">- 申请电报机器人啦~发送<a href=\"post/my-sixth-blog#申请电报机器人啦-发送\"></a></h4><pre><code>/newbot </code></pre><p>给botfather输入机器人名字，以bot结尾，会给一个TOKEN</p>\n<h4 id=\"搭建rss订阅\">- 搭建rss订阅<a href=\"post/my-sixth-blog#搭建rss订阅\"></a></h4><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">wget https://github.com/iovxw/rssbot/releases/download/v1.4.4/rssbot-v1.4.4-linux.zip</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">unzip rssbot-v1.4.4-linux.zip </span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">./rssbot DATAFILE TELEGRAM-BOT-TOKEN</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>最后一句TELEGRAM-BOT-TOKEN替换他给你的，可能会有一点慢，然后等测试完毕没有问题后，可以用nohub命令让机器人在后台运行：nohup ./rssbot DATAFILE TELEGRAM-BOT-TOKEN &gt; /dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1 &amp;</p>\n<h4 id=\"订阅网站\">- 订阅网站<a href=\"post/my-sixth-blog#订阅网站\"></a></h4><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">/rss       - 显示当前订阅的 RSS 列表，加 raw 参数显示链接</span><br><span class=\"line\">/sub       - 订阅一个 RSS: /sub http://example.com/feed.xml</span><br><span class=\"line\">/unsub     - 退订一个 RSS: /unsub http://example.com/feed.xml</span><br><span class=\"line\">/unsubthis - 使用此命令回复想要退订的 RSS 消息即可退订, 不支持 Channel</span><br><span class=\"line\">/export    - 导出为 OPML</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n","next":{"title":"用Aria+AriaNg+rclone+gdrive实现满速下载上传gdrive","link":"post/my-fiveth-blog"},"plink":"http://yoursite.com/post/my-sixth-blog/"}